name: The Museum of UnNatural History
description:
MM collage on canvas, Collection of ZQ Gallery
I animated it using Light Tricks and edited it with sound in Kinemaster.

This NFT features the music of Cut-Out “Schlimmbesserung” 
Cu-Out is a studio project by members of Pell Mell, Robert Beerman, Greg Freeman and Steve Fisk. This music is unreleased and is being used by permission.
